Interface Advice.CallReturn

  • All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public static interface Advice.CallReturn
    A trait to receive the intercepted method return value from Aspecio, as long as Advice.afterPhases() requests the phase PHASE.
